47
00:03:14,390 --> 00:03:15,390
Impian anda?

48
00:03:22,550 --> 00:03:23,790
Tuanku telah mengimpikan saya?

49
00:03:38,710 --> 00:03:41,530
Oleh kerana anda sangat ingin tahu tujuan saya,

50
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:45,850
