mahkamah pagi esok.

62
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,180
Awak patut berehat sekarang.

63
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:32,300
Tidak tergesa-gesa. Kita mempunyai semua masa di dunia.

64
00:04:49,470 --> 00:04:50,470
Jaga kata-kata anda.

65
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:57,040
Hari-hari kita bersama baru bermula.

66
00:04:58,710 --> 00:04:59,710
Betul kata ibu:

67
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:02,010
