180
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,080
Bermimpilah!

181
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,690
Dan saya menemui sesuatu yang penting.

182
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,850
Mendengar adalah salah dan melihat adalah benar.

183
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,440
Jom ikut saya.

184
00:12:49,230 --> 00:12:51,900
Tapi... Puan Yan hanya berehat di sini.

185
00:12:56,470 --> 00:12:59,660
[Dewan Hushan]
Jiang Cha, jaga Istana Ziquan bersama mereka.

186
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:01,810
Jangan sampai sesiapa tahu Puan Yan tidak hadir.

187
00:13:02,510 --> 00:13:03,510
ya.

188
00:13:06,510 --> 00:13:07,416
Chi Anhe dan saya

189
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:09,400
