223
00:14:52,510 --> 00:14:54,900
Wanita syaitan itu baru sahaja
memasuki sisi Sima Jiao.

224
00:14:55,230 --> 00:14:56,296
Kenapa dia

225
00:14:56,320 --> 00:14:57,940
